&lt;li&gt;winstall:https://download.typora.io/windows/typora-setup-ia32-1.6.7.exe&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;picgo&#34;&gt;PicGo&lt;/h2&gt;
